01:23:58.827 --> 01:24:02.038
I believe you.

729
01:24:13.842 --> 01:24:15.593
Tell me about the guardians.

730
01:24:19.723 --> 01:24:21.391
I'm a professional.

731
01:24:22.600 --> 01:24:25.270
I'm a professional. I just do my job.

732
01:24:28.440 --> 01:24:31.609
Tell me about the guardians.

733
01:24:42.287 --> 01:24:43.788
You don't know?

734
01:24:43.872 --> 01:24:45.957
I don't know.

735
01:24:59.053 --> 01:25:01.556
He works the door at a rave in Neza.

736
01:25:01.639 --> 01:25:02.682
He has a mark

737
01:25:02.766 --> 01:25:04.726
on the left side of his face.

738
01:25:04.809 --> 01:25:07.187
They call him The Butcher.

739
01:25:08.396 --> 01:25:09.481
Is he La Hermandad?

740
01:25:09.898 --> 01:25:12.192
